snippet.title: Synapse - Teaser Trailer | PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
Watch the teaser trailer for Synapse, the new VR action game from the award-winning team behind Fracked and Phantom: Covert Ops.

Fight through a hostile mindscape in the immersive next-gen experience created exclusively for PlayStation VR2. Turn the mind into a battlefield and unleash your inner anti-hero with brutal firepower in one hand and surging telekinesis in the other.

Coming 2023. 

#psvr2 #psvr2games #stateofplay
